members.name: Credential.iconURL
members.description: Returns a DOMString containing the URL of an image for the credential. The URL must be from a secure context.

members.name: Credential.id
members.description: Returns a DOMString containing the credential's identifier. This might be any one of a GUID, username, or email address.

members.name: Credential.name
members.description: ReturnsÂ a DOMString containing a name associated with the credential. This is intended to be a human-readable public name.

members.name: Credential.type
members.description: Returns a DOMString containing the credential's type. Valid values are password and federated.
